Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:42.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}誰が決めたんだ　そんな生き方らしくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:48.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}やりたいこと貫く力　それこそが強さだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:52.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}分かっているから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:01.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}歩んできた日々を　懐かしむ意味を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:10.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}諦めることはない　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:19.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}心の光を　覚えてるうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:23.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:28.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain 抹去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:26.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely 故事總在隻言片語間展開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:28.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}無論怎麼做都無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}但不要忘記你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:42.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}別人定義出的你 不是真實的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:48.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}堅持自我的力量 才是真的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:52.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}這就是我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:01.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會回憶走過的路 找出價值所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:10.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會堅持到最後 不會放棄
